{"tid":738630,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"歐美將聯手批評中國未有履行世貿義務","createTime":"2018-07-11T16:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T01:00:19.000Z","uid":13663,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2684e61b70800a887e547996671d3312c9f9625c","tid":738630,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T16:08:28.000Z","msg":"6小時前  Share to Facebook<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】世界貿易組織成員國今日起一連三日在瑞士日內瓦開會。消息透露，歐洲將會加入美國行列，批評中國未有履行世貿義務。<br />\n<br />\n面對美國向全球挑起貿易戰，中國一度希望同歐洲聯手對抗美國。不過消息透露，歐洲無意與中國聯手，反而將在會上加入批評中國的行列，指中國在鋼材鋁材上產能過盛，導致全球鋼鋁價格大跌。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟同時認為，中國存在不公平的技術轉讓，在保護知識產權的工作上明顯不足，通過補貼破壞全球貿易規則。<br />\n<br />\n中國則會強調，在加入世貿組織後已履行責任對外開放市場，降低了關稅和貿易壁疊、維護自由貿易和多邊體制。"},{"pid":"035aeb63a849d4ea7a5862285c5bdeadbdd77cb7","tid":738630,"uid":13663,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T16:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/001053_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F001053_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=c397ceb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d67eaba22f1f00b9b8a225a56c5073312ebff08a","tid":738630,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T16:25:54.000Z","msg":"不問價入熊"},{"pid":"9f5ea46d9037cdb1e51dc70436f7a36ad5bcafd2","tid":738630,"uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T16:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/003117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F003117_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2c864665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83dfe27360fb79f3b7b515ae33dff2fd8f3c1f6e","tid":738630,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T16:39:56.